This is the official video for the '2025 Why Samsung Home Appliances.'

Discover how Samsung Home Appliances stand out through four core values: Bespoke AI, SmartThings, Knox Security, and Reliability.
Bespoke AI enhances functionality and convenience, making daily tasks easier and more efficient. SmartThings seamlessly connects and integrates into your lifestyle, offering effortless convenience and smart home experiences. Knox Security provides triple-layered protection, ensuring robust security and peace of mind. 
Reliability ensures durability with extreme testing, 7 years of software updates, and industry-leading warranties and Home Appliance Remote Management, ensuring durability and peace of mind.

Learn more: http://www.samsung.com
